397
00:41:36,960 --> 00:41:38,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, neće biti to sporno, ništa.

398
00:41:38,320 --> 00:41:39,599
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, sve će biti.

399
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:48,719
